Domains2IDNA
=============

Python module/library to convert a domain or a file with a list of domain to the famous IDNA format.

By Funilrys http://github.com/funilrys


Features
=============
 * Read a file and convert each line to IDNA.
 * Read a given domain and return it in IDNA format.
 * Write result into a file

Usage example
=============

>>> # This save the output into 'translators.json' in your current location
>>> from domain2idna.core import Core
>>> print(Core('bittréẋ.com').to_idna())

For more please report to https://github.com/funilrys/domain2idna
